main event: A round, silver, solid object was sighted hanging and bobbing in the sky, observed from Winter, Wisconsin.
interesting points: The object was visually observed for a duration of 15-20 minutes., The object's movement involved back and forth oscillation., It was seen changing direction while a moon was rising in the east., The object was initially described as having a balloon-like appearance., The incident was recorded on a Project 10073 record card as part of Project Blue Book.
